<title type="html"><![CDATA[Heosphoros (pouet) - background]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=5371&amp;p=48583#p48583"><![CDATA[
The Embered Recollections rom uses three 4k chr banks per image and switches them mid-frame with help of the <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/MMC3" class="postlink">MMC3</a> scanline counter.<br />It's an awful waste of chr space (compared to what NES games used back in the day), but it works for demo type projects I guess.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1377">miau</a> — Mon Jul 06, 2009 3:20 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
